  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Identify and analyze static equilibrium situations</item>
<item>Set up a free-body diagram for an extended object in static equilibrium</item>
<item>Set up and solve static equilibrium conditions for objects in equilibrium in various physical situations</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
